about.summary: Provides a hash table class for fast key-value storage of atomic vector types.

name: r-hashmap
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.2.2" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-hashmap
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/hashmap_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/hashmap/hashmap_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 1280f387a53de0185d6aee15094b7d2929ec30493b9702a6ec328f01a2afd7e3

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 1002
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}      # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-bh
    - r-rcpp >=0.12.4
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-bh
    - r-rcpp >=0.12.4

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('hashmap')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('hashmap')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/nathan-russell/hashmap
  license: MIT
  summary: Provides a hash table class for fast key-value storage of atomic vector types.
  license_family: MIT

  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/MIT
    - LICENSE
extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
